{
  "stem": "16792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the little brother was always with me, I mean, whenever I go someplace, and that's all that it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We was five children, and we was brought up very, very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitler came to power in 1933.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember I was-- it was on a Friday someplace, in-- in Oswiecim, I was in the center of the market.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're calling it a market, the center space.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I heard that Hitler [INAUDIBLE] that Hitler came to power in Germany, and this is the way it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we was talking about Hitler before that, too, you see, when he wrote Mein Kampf and all kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was that he hates Jews and all kinds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, we find out before that-- before that, and before 1933-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before 1933-- it was 1931 or something-- I-- I got-- my father's got a sister which lived in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her husband was a lawyer, an attorney, and he came-- he-- he run away from-- from Germany, and he came to Oswiecim, because all family is in Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father and my grandfather, he bring some money with him, but not too much, and he opened up a big store, a very big store, from-- from-- how do you call the peddle?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bicycle?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bicycles, very big, and he was doing very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for this we know what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Friday night, we meet all of-- all the family met by my grandfather every Friday night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was talking, talking, and he-- he told me that what happened in Germany, that Hitler came, and he took away a lot of stuff from him, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sure, we know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We know everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Middle class.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She give a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
